Package com.paypal.selion.platform.web

This package houses all the classes related to parsing the GUI Object map to create SeLion specific Page Objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GuiMapReader
    Interface which all PageObject "GUI Map" providers must implement.
    ProcessGuiMap
    This interface represents the abilities of any concrete implementation that deals with parsing GUI Object map for creating the SeLion Page Objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GUIElement
    This page represents the Web elements on a Page
    GuiMapReaderFactory
    This reader Factory returns the reader instance depending on the type of input data file.
    HtmlContainerElement
    This object represents a Web element within a Container element.
    Page
    This class represents the PageYaml V2 file.
